'''Blackmoon Eleven''' was a designation used by a pilot within [[Blackmoon Squadron]]. As of [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]], Blackmoon Eleven was [[Koril Bekam]]. He was in a [[Bacta tank/Legends|bacta tank]] during the evacuation of [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]], however, and [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] used his fighter to escape the world. Its comm unit was damaged such that it could broadcast its transponder signal, but no voice traffic. Thus, Antilles flew anonymously in the battle, in which he engaged and defeated more than a squadron of [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]].

